evidence.source_document: Notice of Voluntary Dismissal Without Prejudice
evidence.text: Plaintiffs voluntarily dismiss this action without prejudice. If Defendants later transfer Bureau funds in contradiction of their repeated representations... Plaintiffs will undertake further actions as appropriate.

evidence.source_document: Complaint for Injunctive and Declaratory Relief
evidence.text: The complaint alleges violations of the APA in two counts, challenging the Acting Director's request of zero dollars from the Board of Governors, combined with an alleged decision and attempt to return CFPB's existing operating and reserve funds to the Federal Reserve.
